title: Dr. Dan
description:
Kirk Minihane and his brother Ryan relive the horrors they endured as innocent children suffering in the hands of Dr. Arthur Daniels, a.k.a. The Toothman.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kminshow
